text: Dzintars Jaundžeikars (14 February 1956 – 16 March 2022) was a Latvian politician. He was a member of the LPP/LC and a deputy from 2002 until 2010. Jaundžeikars was also Minister of the Interior of Latvia from 3 November 2005 to 7 November 2006. Jaundžeikars died on 16 March 2022 at the age of 66.Mūžībā devies eksministrs Dzintars Jaundžeikars ==References== Category:1956 births Category:2022 deaths Category:Latvian politicians
